snippet.title: CARNE VESCENS - Launch Trailer | PSX-Style Indie Horror Game
snippet.description:
Trapped in her own apartment, a mother finds herself unable to keep her insatiable baby fed.

So she decides to feed her baby the only bit of food she has left: HERSELF.

"Carne Vescens" is a short psychological horror game about motherhood and neverending parental love in the style of late 90s PSX-games.

Download the full game completely for free:
https://out-of-the-ordinary-world.itch.io/carne-vescens

Features:

- Features audio in CD quality and even Full Motion Videos!

- Full Controller support (Xbox 360/One/Series) featuring two control schemes, old school D-Pad centric or a more modern dual stick layout.

- Do whatever every good mother would do: Take care of your baby, no matter the costs.
